	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm not very practiced with drawn art (I drew more comics and stuff when I was 13), but I've had a lot of fun with this site:
<br /><a href="http://www.brokenpicturetelephone.com/" class="postlink">http://www.brokenpicturetelephone.com/</a>
<br />It usually loads really, really slow, but it's worth it.
<br />
<br />It's a game where you draw a pic from a description, or write a description of a picture.  10 minute time limit.  So things get misinterpreted and changed into all sorta of strange things.
<br />
<br />I found it fun to get into drawing these random things, here are <a href="http://www.brokenpicturetelephone.com/players/memblers/games/?type=drawings&amp;p=1" class="postlink">my drawings</a>.  If you click on one, it'll go to the game it was involved in.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
